'From Squeak3.5 of ''11 April 2003'' [latest update: #5180] on 21 August 2004 at 12:00:10 pm'!"Change Set:		ExpandedPublishing-dgdDate:			16 March 2004Author:			Diego Gomez Deck <DiegoGomezDeck@ConsultAr.com>New preference to present the project publishing dialog in expanded mode by default."Preferences	addPreference: #expandedPublishing	category: #publishing	default: true	balloonHelp: 'If true, the project publishing dialog appear in expanded mode'.!!EToyProjectDetailsMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'dgd 3/16/2004 12:10'!expandedFormat	^ Preferences expandedPublishing			or: [self valueOfProperty: #expandedFormat ifAbsent: [false]]! !